soon. It is essential that you should make yourself believe I’m really dead. As things stand it won’t be very far from the truth, as my brother is part of my soul.”

“I’d do anything,” she said, “anything for his sake and yours. Only I’m dreadfully frightened, and it is all getting mixed up in my head.”

